{"result": {"folders": ["lecture21"], "nr": 1318, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2019-04-30T14:15:48Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "isysgjh9fxf7a6", "data": "jv3vjj7s9rofp", "type": "create", "when": "2019-04-30T14:15:48Z"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "jj4coowv6Wrm", "to": "jv3vjj7pfqlfo", "type": "followup", "when": "2019-05-12T00:03:23Z"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "isysgjh9fxf7a6", "subject": "lec21视频7中RAID在线练习的问题", "created": "2019-04-30T14:15:48Z", "content": "<p>题目如下&#xff1a;</p>\n<p>关于冗余磁盘阵列(RAID, Redundant Array of Inexpensive Disks)的阐述正确的是&#xff1a;</p>\n<ul><li>[x] 采用RAID机制可提高磁盘IO的吞吐量(通过并行)</li><li>[x] 采用RAID机制可提高磁盘IO的可靠性和可用性 (通过冗余)</li><li>[ ] 采用RAID-0可提高磁盘IO的可靠性和可用性</li><li>[ ] 采用RAID-1可提高磁盘IO的吞吐量</li></ul>\n<p></p>\n<p>解释是&#xff1a;「RAID-0提高并行性&#xff0c;RAID-1提高可靠性」</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>我对最后一个选项有疑惑&#xff1a;虽然 RAID-1 是简单复制&#xff0c;但在读取时可以利用此特性&#xff0c;并发读取&#xff0c;因此我认为也提高磁盘 I/O 的吞吐量。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>查到一些实际测试的例子&#xff0c;其中不同条件下 RAID-1 的读取速度有 9% 到 50% 的提升&#xff1a;https://macperformanceguide.com/Storage-RAID1-speed.html</p>"}], "type": "question", "tags": ["lecture21", "student", "unanswered"], "tag_good": [], "unique_views": 77, "children": [{"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "no_upvotes": 0, "subject": "我认为raid1确实会提高读性能&#xff0c;但是写性能还是一样的&#xff0c;I/O吞吐量取决于其中较小的一个&#xff0c;所以并不会提高。", "created": "2019-05-12T00:03:23Z", "bucket_order": 46, "bucket_name": "Week 5/12 - 5/18", "type": "followup", "tag_good": [], "uid": "jj4coowv6Wrm", "children": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "jvk6djrlp742kp", "updated": "2019-05-12T00:03:23Z", "config": {}}], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 1, "id": "jv3vjj7pfqlfo", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "bookmarked": 2, "num_favorites": 1, "my_favorite": false, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "s_edits"